#: ../../index.rst:2
msgid "AgentSociety 2"
msgstr "AgentSociety 2"

#: ../../index.rst:4
msgid ""
"**AgentSociety 2** 是一个现代化的、LLM 原生的智能体模拟平台，专为社会科学研究和实验设计。它提供了一个灵活的框架，用于在模拟环境中创建和管理智能智能体。"
msgstr ""
"**AgentSociety 2** is a modern, LLM-native agent simulation platform designed for "
"social science research and experimental design. It provides a flexible framework "
"for creating and managing intelligent agents in simulated environments."

#: ../../index.rst:6
msgid "PyPI Version"
msgstr "PyPI Version"

