msgstr "Python Versions"

#: ../../index.rst:14
msgid "License"
msgstr "License"

#: ../../index.rst:19
msgid "核心特性"
msgstr "Key Features"

#: ../../index.rst:21
msgid "**LLM 驱动的智能体**: 创建具有个性、记忆和推理能力的智能智能体，由大语言模型驱动。"
msgstr ""
"**LLM-Powered Agents**: Create intelligent agents with personalities, memories, and "
"reasoning capabilities, powered by large language models."

#: ../../index.rst:23
msgid "**灵活的环境模块**: 使用可组合的工具和状态管理构建自定义模拟环境。"
msgstr ""
"**Flexible Environment Modules**: Build custom simulation environments with "
"composable tools and state management."

#: ../../index.rst:25
msgid "**异步优先设计**: 高性能异步架构，实现高效的多智能体模拟。"
msgstr ""
"**Async-First Design**: High-performance asynchronous architecture for efficient "
"multi-agent simulations."

#: ../../index.rst:27
msgid "**回放与分析**: 基于 SQLite 的内置存储，用于实验跟踪和分析。"
msgstr ""
"**Replay and Analysis**: Built-in SQLite-based storage for experiment tracking "
"and analysis."

#: ../../index.rst:29
msgid "**研究技能**: 内置文献检索、假设生成、实验设计、论文撰写等 LLM 原生工作流。"
msgstr ""
"**Research Skills**: Built-in LLM-native workflows for literature search, hypothesis "
"generation, experiment design, and paper writing."

#: ../../index.rst:31
msgid "**REST API**: 基于 FastAPI 的独立后端服务，支持外部集成。"
msgstr ""
"**REST API**: Independent FastAPI-based backend service for external integrations."

#: ../../index.rst:33
msgid "**CLI 工具**: 强大的命令行界面，支持实验运行和进度跟踪。"
msgstr ""
"**CLI Tool**: Powerful command-line interface for experiment execution and progress tracking."

#: ../../index.rst:35
msgid "**可扩展**: 轻松扩展自定义智能体、环境和工具。"
msgstr ""
"**Extensible**: Easily extend with custom agents, environments, and tools."

